headline: One More Thing About List Binary Search
description:
I wanted to point people to this link at DotNetPearls:
http://www.dotnetperls.com/binarysearchThey do an excellent, quick demonstration of List&lt;T&gt;.BinarySearch and show a graph that really drives home how much faster it is for large lists than a regular traversal!
headline_zh-Hans: 关于列表二进制搜索的另一件事
headline_zh-Hant: 關於列表二進制搜索的另一件事

http://www.dotnetperls.com/binarysearchThey 对List&lt;T&gt;.BinarySearch做了一个很好的快速演示，并展示了一个图表，该图表真正体现了它对大型列表的速度比普通的遍历要快得多!
